nd workshops.
\par <#/>Take the example of the Institute of Production Innovation, IPI, an institute of the University of Dar es Salaam affiliated to the Faculty of Engineering. <#/>During the past five or six years the institute has succeeded to develop a numb
er of technologies, some of which have diffused into the local market.
\par <#/>These include village oil processing technology, corn mills and hullers, feed mills and mixers, block-making and improvised industrial maintenance.
\par <#/>In spite of <-_there><+_the
